Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库大人  醒了么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.87,0:00:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒是醒了  但慢慢起床的时间还是有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是Union Fasta的最后一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城里面又是热闹得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.39,0:00:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定很热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.36,0:00:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典要结束了好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快乐的时光就不能一直持续下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.68,0:00:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.24,0:00:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:31.75,logo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,00)\pos(370,220)\be50}「FinalStage」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.38,0:02:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送还三位勇者的预定日期定在了Union Fasta结束之后的三天后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.29,0:02:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离别之日马上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀…谢谢你蕾贝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.56,0:02:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还特意过来送我一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天七海和公主大人去了比斯科迪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.97,0:02:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真久和库蓓尔在帕斯提亚久
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.36,0:02:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我去伽雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉就好像是互换勇者似的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.13,0:02:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.42,0:02:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说我准备了点有趣的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七海和米尔希那边肯定会很欢乐的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾贝卡你不来一件么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  现在为您进行现场直播
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Union Fasta的谈话节目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.11,0:03:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时段的舞台嘉宾是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比斯科迪共和国代表领主  米尔希奥蕾公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.58,0:03:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:19.18,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伽雷特狮子团杰诺瓦兹的三位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是这位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比斯科迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比斯科迪的勇者  高槻七海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…那个  勇者大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么感觉和平时不太一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实呢  趁着这个机会  今天七海来当我的勇者了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说一日勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾恩殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Union Fasta也到了最后一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次活动的直到现在的结果怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:04:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无疑问  到现在为止的成绩非常的好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高尔殿下  那么对于勇者大人您怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁这个机会问她本人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我国勇者在此登场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好  我是伽雷特的勇者蕾贝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天蕾贝卡是我伽雷特的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exmachina也当然是仿造品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾贝卡大人好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七海大人和蕾贝卡大人都扮演的很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说勇者大人将成为帕斯提亚久的一日勇者喽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说衣服也都换成这边的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔♂法♂光♂线
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.01,0:04:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这必然不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:04:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒…倒也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得…在各种意义上都算擦边球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…大家这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  倒是挺合身嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细一想必然是这种结果嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真久  很帅的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.11,0:05:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  到了勇者们该回去的时间了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  很快就会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怀念啊  地球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们回去的时候我能不能一起去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个还用说？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边女孩的体型和内衣都是什么样的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风太大没听清  什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.51,0:05:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:06:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才对嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  今晚的Final Stage敬请大家期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.04,0:06:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？诺瓦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.03,0:06:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和诺瓦还有莉科  现在要出个门
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我们送一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.16,0:06:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  没事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.05,0:06:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们三个乘飞毯过去轻松得很
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.77,0:06:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  米尔希姐的演唱会前再见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞毯  走起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来我们也往会场那边走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕斯提亚久正统继承者生物模式确认
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时确认天枪Coumars装备
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门即将打开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是艾森巴哈城的地下传承宝物库
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为帕斯提亚久引以为傲的古代遗址  是个超大型迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾有所耳闻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是第一次能进到里头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.54,0:07:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩以前不是跟我说过想要在这里探险吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是很小的时候的事儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.59,0:07:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的信条就是约好了就决不会忘也不会食言嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢  一定要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个宝物库有很多对付入侵者的陷阱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.44,0:07:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  只有地下才会有陷阱的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一楼的陷阱已经全部关闭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的库大人  不要吓我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是库大人你自己难道有什么事么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我本来是来取送还仪式上要送给蕾贝卡的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的回忆之物就放在这里面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:07:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后莉科和诺瓦  你们不是经历了上次的勇者送还吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想听听那个时候发生了什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个宝箱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先先拿好这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞毯飞毯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辉力开放·七尾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好悬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦  好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,设置了陷阱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这个地方已经很旧了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:08:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么地方出了些问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是地下十层吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是垂直掉下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用飞毯的话很快就能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  关上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被关在这里了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有地图
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看那个的话肯定能找到通往出口的路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.72,0:09:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位  踩在地板上的时候一定要多加注意…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我话还没说完就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这迷宫太累人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不赶紧出去…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好这里有椅子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.09,0:10:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是这个难道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾贝卡  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.55,0:10:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.64,0:10:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.55,0:10:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了  总有种不好的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.99,0:10:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岔路口  有个岔路口就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.74,0:10:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管前面怎么跑都是一条路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？贝琪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真久  库大人跟你们汇合了么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…还没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.65,0:11:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不是那么费时间的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城堡的地下？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是要去地下的宝物库
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个宝物库啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个地方原本是我作为魔王的时候建造的迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里头布满各种各样的邪恶残忍的陷阱  是超赞的最终迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了  陷阱都锁住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢  毕竟那些东西也有些年头了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:11:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝琪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没路了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那么我们稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉科  诺瓦  真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.27,0:12:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我把你们请来这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库大人  你这说的就不对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本想要来这里的是我们才对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如果我能够再小心谨慎一些就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是当初仔细打理这个地方就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.95,0:12:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要那么说的话  还得怪我当时你们刚掉下去的时候我没能用七尾把你们抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也在想如果当时能多多注意一下地面的陷阱就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.04,0:12:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的  这是城堡的地下  到时候肯定会有人来救咱们的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  话说库大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于送还的事情你想问我们什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有在和勇者分别的时候感到寂寞或者感到不安什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.90,0:13:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是非常的寂寞和悲伤的  我哭了好长时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次的送还也发生了很多很多的事情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.97,0:13:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢  当知道了他还能再回来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞的感觉就全部都消失不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对于七海和真久要回去的事情也感到很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但说真的  不知道什么时候就又能见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢  果然这过程还是会很不安的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾贝卡是远方世界的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.71,0:13:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在故乡也有很多有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有很多很多重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会直接忘了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.26,0:14:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不  我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.35,0:14:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾贝卡是个温柔的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也明白那种事情是不会发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.14,0:14:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢  别离还是很伤感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就尽管笑话我这个不值得信赖的  胆小又稚嫩的见习领主吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.16,0:14:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会笑话你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟最喜欢的人分别却不感到寂寞的人  这个世界上是不存在的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  莉科  休息结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就到这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送还蕾贝卡大人之前剩下来的这点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了你们两个人能待在一起更长的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧从这里出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉科  诺瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.84,0:14:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易我耍一回帅  别这样对我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:14:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  逃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不掉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个  快看上面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我争取想想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能让我的两个好朋友受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Coumars所在位置确认
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱暂时停止但撑不了太长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真久  蕾贝卡  快去救援
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.62,0:15:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘  拿着这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.75,0:15:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔人结晶  也就是说是英雄结晶的魔王版
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾贝卡的话肯定能用好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.48,0:15:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者  传送
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又开始掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.31,0:16:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能打开这扇门…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.98,0:16:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者真久的英雄时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者蕾贝卡现在抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.69,0:16:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾贝卡  真久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.01,0:16:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就把这东西给推回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事  这东西好沉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真久  你先一个人支撑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:17:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔人结晶  发动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔人模式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔女加农炮·超魔王模式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.26,0:17:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  快卧倒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我飞！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  真久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:28.53,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾贝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾贝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.52,0:18:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我早说过了要去危险的地方的时候一定要由我和骑士们同行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你没事儿真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姑且也算是骑士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦  小声哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.58,0:19:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  快点从这里离开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人的演唱会快要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了正式开幕的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.80,0:19:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有五分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在刚才大家都入座了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.44,0:19:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  大家没事儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点问题都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在欢笑中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我也就安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我先回座位了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.96,0:23:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在帕斯提亚久当一天的勇者服…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.02,0:23:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对啊这是贝琪的！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.19,0:23:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是谢谢大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.30,0:23:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种弹性  真不愧是…啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
