Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.97,0:01:34.81,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}仿佛在寻找那飘渺的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.93,0:01:35.61,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}FEARLESS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:40.29,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我还要变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.41,0:01:45.70,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不是为了回忆  而是为了眼前的你
